---
title: Smoky Adobo Chicken Tacos with Mango Slaw & Lime Crema
description: Chipotle adobo sauce makes the perfect one-ingredient marinade - especially if you love deep, smoky flavours. Cool lime crema, creamy avocado, and tangy mango slaw help to balance out the heat in these irresistible tacos.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smoky-adobo-chicken-tacos-8b4567.jpg
